parser.ast

Class Coalition

  • java.lang.Object
    • parser.ast.Coalition

  • public class Coalition
extends java.lang.Object
    Class to represent coalition info, e.g., in an ExpressionStrategy object. Stored as a list of strings which are either player names (e.g. "controller") or player indices (e.g. "2"). Alternatively, "*" denotes all players.
